snippet.title: Naruto Gekito Ninja Taisen 4 English Mod v1.1 Released (VERSION 1.2 AVAILABLE)
snippet.description:
Version 1.2 Download: https://www.mediafire.com/file/lmfe3cvne0zf8y4/GNT4_-_v1.2.1.zip/file

Mod Download (v1.1): https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1-ihRv6OhQbb-OIE5i4pG22ZqX7ZbWZtE?usp=sharing

Here it is! The english voice mod with the GNT4 exclusive stuff is here (Sound 5, 3rd Hokage, Unites). Have fun with this mod! Future versions will just have some minor audio fixes if I have to make them.

Thank you Zirotho and BradLeeTee for providing Ultimate Ninja Storm 4 sound clips!

Join the Clash of Ninja Community!: https://discord.gg/Kz9Ypzg

Join my discord server to get updates about my future projects!: https://discord.gg/6rJa3em
